mass - 				The mass of the ring that was mapped, in megatonnes 
outerradius - 		The outer radius of the ring that was mapped, in kilometers 
probesused - 		The number of probes used to map the ring 
reserves - 			The reserve level of the ring that was mapped, if the parent body has already been scanned 
ringname - 			The name of the ring that was mapped
_}

